      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          <span>Can I practice nursing in India with this degree?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Your European BSc Nursing degree is recognized. You need to register with the Indian Nursing Council (INC), which involves document verification and sometimes a screening test. We guide you through every step.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          <span>What if I don't like it abroad and want to come back?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Your degree is valid in India. Complete your INC registration and you can practice at any hospital in India — Apollo, Fortis, government hospitals. Many of our graduates work in India after completing their degree abroad.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          <span>Is Gradiks a registered agency? Do you take money from universities?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Gradiks is a registered study-abroad consultancy. We do NOT take commissions from universities. Our recommendations are based on your profile and goals — not on which university pays us more. This is why we can be honest about pros and cons.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          <span>How is this different from other consultancies?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We tell you the full picture — costs, registration process, what exams you'll need after graduation — before you pay anything. Most consultancies hide the hard parts until after you've committed. We give you the honest assessment first.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-toggle" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          <span>What happens after graduation — exactly what exams do I need?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
